metadata.name: RED
metadata.description:
RED is probably one of the most complicated colors. It is powerful, eye-catching, it has been used by humans for thousands years.

In different cultures it is the color of power, love, beauty & death.

Red is powerful yet feminine. It can be either warm or cold, like every woman. So I couldn't depict it as just a pretty woman.  
My red lady is calm & tender, but may go to extremes if needed.  
She looks mature and dreamy, she has gone through hardships that made her wiser. She is strong, self-confident, patient, kind & embracing.

The kind of mother I hope to be one day.

Red is controversial like the life itself. Itâ€™s up to you to decide whether it is a red carpet or a red flag.

Traditional gouache art, 2022.
